name: She Dervish 2021
description:
Digitized a section of a 2011 and created “She Dervish” 

The owl is typically linked with female energies due to its long slender neck which resembles fertility goddesses like Isis or Ishtar who symbolize motherhood but the owl has not always only been associated with women either.

Sound design by @fendelmarc Recorded and mixed 10/2021 Spitfire LABS & Korg NTS 1
